            . The 24th of July, Downing and another person came to my shop with 12 silver coat buttons to pawn, I lent him 15 s. upon them; they being in my custody, the prosecutor came to search, and I knowing Mr. Welch, the other person who came with Downing, he directed me where to find him.</p>
